      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should see a doctor but i really cant right now, like i'm stuck at work all day and it's so expensive to go to a clinic mid-week. i've taken the 400mg before and it's fine, i don't feel sick. i just want to know if the frequent dosing logic makes sense because once it wears off the pain is unbearable. if i just do 400mg every 2 hours for like a day, is that really going to hurt me that much?",
